  "text": "As these different processes may have different therapeutic implications it is crucial to learn which are at work. To understand better what MATH is capturing at a cellular and molecular level, we are working with colleagues who have developed methods for teasing out the contributions of normal DNA, overall changes in DNA ploidy, more localized CNA, and subclonal somatic point mutations to the observed MAF values in a tumor. [CITATION_1] ",
